author: Alexander Stoklosa
title: Spied! 2018 Subaru Ascent Three-Row CUV Sheds Camo
text:
- What It Is: The crossover destined to be Subaru ’s largest vehicle when it joins the lineup late this year or early next year. With three rows of seating and exterior dimensions similar to those of the Honda Pilot, the Ford Explorer, and other family haulers, the Ascent is the spiritual—and far less bizarre—successor to the Tribeca that you forgot Subaru sold from 2006 to 2014.
